answers.answer: Go back and see your doctor again. Have them run some other tests to see what's going on. No one here can tell you what's happening with your body.
Have they done any kind of ultrasound be sure?

question: Hi, I had my last period on July 27th and after I got sealed to my husband on August 7th we started trying for a baby. I haven't had a period since but have been having many pregnancy symptoms. I took about 6 HPT all negative the doctor did 4 urine tests and a blood test on the 4th all negative and no thyroid problems, diabetes or any other problems. Can I still be pregnant or is there another reason I'm missing?
title: Pregnant?
